{"tid":1516513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學聯殺到，民間記者會可以停得未？","createTime":"2019-08-29T14:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T12:57:32.000Z","uid":50286,"like":99,"dislike":182,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"adf1981bd045763ad9953d98b54f40e5304a1488","tid":1516513,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:54:53.000Z","msg":"我知上次學po好多人屌鳩我<br />\n但我要重申<br />\n我地監管到記者會嘅內容，但係監管唔到發言義士嘅決定或ego會否膨脹。<br />\n<br />\n依個都唔係重點。<br />\n<br />\n今次佢哋玩到出咗學聯！<br />\n<br />\n大家睇睇2014年，學聯做咗啲乜嘢就心中有數啦！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">呢一步點都係錯。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算民間記者會繼續，我哋都唔應該再侵學聯玩，唔好理佢地講任何野！<br />\n要好似上次支瘋話：舉手！<br />\n大家都睬佢有味咁<br />\n<br />\n記住秉承<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無大台</span></span>嘅宗旨！<br />\n<br />\n大不了就攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ff56c7a91aefb928a3ebd2cd30fb2abf4f51a58","tid":1516513,"uid":218313,"like":29,"dislike":10,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n認同雨革核心人物唔應該扑咪<br />\n好易招人話柄"},{"pid":"824cf7ee4e45855038ef9f88ba3f3d3544deb6ee","tid":1516513,"uid":250444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，阻你小小位！<br />\n但係我地唔可以白廢兄弟既心機！<br />\n<br />\n畢架山 直幡 (有片)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1516468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1516468</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1c3cc447ad3683dba731c7b769bc4bed19f1ff5a","tid":1516513,"uid":151256,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"佢都係出嚟做人版呼籲啫，畀個大台佢哋都唔敢做啦"},{"pid":"183773aed8f7c675f246cf7db295f4be76d83fdf","tid":1516513,"uid":119283,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"你地有無睇哂條片先？睇完都仲覺有問題？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uXm3bHQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuXm3bHQ.gif&h=2f88ca55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b77cf79107cf5188a7d28e9028d5df97cdc73d5","tid":1516513,"uid":231818,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"673fff52f695e29c8226336ccd9725e1f87015f7","tid":1516513,"uid":26970,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"如果你有睇 請講出邊到係有大台之勢<br />\n唔好因人廢言"},{"pid":"d3a735d6d987706dd5551cd255556b3114f173bd","tid":1516513,"uid":12510,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其實樓主有冇睇晒個記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4c28203a11d23d8fa4316de4d298bafd6fc75fda","tid":1516513,"uid":4001,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"你睇撚左先講啦話人大台，成碌柒咁"},{"pid":"3e2750a1aae2b1f6e0ce6e104fd9ffd065865bac","tid":1516513,"uid":148987,"like":8,"dislike":19,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:02:20.000Z","msg":"上都算<br />\n唔好幾個一齊<br />\n又梁又岑想點<br />\n有騎劫feel<br />\n講明民間比d冇政治聯繫<br />\n學聯d人咁出名自已開個記招都得啦屌"},{"pid":"eee53295d78a0a5e7bd6c80edd39a499ab1f181c","tid":1516513,"uid":4001,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"冇撚睇就成個藍絲廢老咁岀黎搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864956fe1866518604f96e4ee692ddeb12421243","tid":1516513,"uid":81996,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sco